'''鬚後水'''是[[男性|男性]]在剃鬚之後於剃過的部位塗的一種液體。可能含有[[變性酒精|變性酒精]]等[[抗菌劑|抗菌劑]]以免剃後感染，但因為使用了酒精的緣故也會使得人感覺到一種燒灼感，這種感覺可能會持續幾分鐘。<ref>{{cite web
 |url         = http://site.groominglounge.com/images/press58.htm
 |title       = Soothe Yourself
 |publisher   = GQ
 |accessdate  = 2007-11-08
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20071123002240/http://site.groominglounge.com/images/press58.htm
 |archivedate =2007-11-23|deadurl     = yes
}}</ref> 剃鬚水的使用可追溯至[[古羅馬|古羅馬]]時代，<ref>{{cite web|author=Modern Gent |url=http://www.moderngent.com/history_of_shaving/history_of_shaving.php |title=The History of Shaving |publisher=Moderngent.com |date= |accessdate=2012-10-20}}</ref> 因為常與[[古龍水|古龍水]]成份相似，二者易被混淆。

早期的鬚後水包括[[金縷梅|金縷梅酊劑]]和[[月桂油|月桂油]]，這些物質至今仍然被用作鬚後水的原料。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.archive.org/details/shavingmadeeasyw0020th |title=Shaving made easy; what the man who shaves ought to know .. : 20th century correspondence school, New York. [from old catalog] : Free Download & Streaming : Internet Archive |publisher=Archive.org |date=2001-03-10 |accessdate=2012-10-20}}</ref>

